{"tid":2054381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何依婷曾收狂迷下體照騷擾：問我「想要嗎？」好核突唔敢睇！","createTime":"2020-06-07T06:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T13:28:25.000Z","uid":1426,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4941fd51ce176d27636d12125fd080cc54a9ecd7","tid":2054381,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"何依婷（Regina）昨晚（4/6）現身將軍澳電視城出席《萬眾同心公益金》項目「齊心打氣有鼓勵」綵排。憑劇集《機場特警》演「絕世港女」角色人氣火速爆紅，成為新一代宅男女神，IG粉絲人數更不斷攀升，仲突破超過13萬。<br />\n<br />\n不過成功背後，卻引來狂迷傳露械照騷擾 ，令Regina苦不堪言：「其實唔同嘅訊息我都會睇，試過打開其中個訊息嘅時候，就睇到一張男性嘅性器官相，嗰一刻我好驚唔敢睇，連下面啲留言訊息我都唔敢望，其實喺有啲核突，嗰一刻真係要洗眼，其實我都唔只收過一次，而且有啲留言都好騷擾，佢哋會出言挑逗，會留言話：『想要嗎？』諗起都覺得好核突，咁所以希望大家保暖，唔好除咁多。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200605/345543469000953856.jpeg/RFkbpAylAR6D-80C3eM_jfl_ULBNfGoh_-G5v__hub8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200605%2F345543469000953856.jpeg%2FRFkbpAylAR6D-80C3eM_jfl_ULBNfGoh_-G5v__hub8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=44640526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/482064/何依婷曾收狂迷下體照騷擾-問我-想要嗎-好核突唔敢睇\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F482064%2F%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%9D%E5%A9%B7%E6%9B%BE%E6%94%B6%E7%8B%82%E8%BF%B7%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E7%85%A7%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-%E5%95%8F%E6%88%91-%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E5%97%8E-%E5%A5%BD%E6%A0%B8%E7%AA%81%E5%94%94%E6%95%A2%E7%9D%87&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=9ca9c948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/482064/何依婷曾收狂迷下體照騷擾-問我-想要嗎-好核突唔敢睇</a>"},{"pid":"c24fbf52b89a7586764e3a3ac42952e1ea5bf949","tid":2054381,"uid":1426,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200605/345380073999831040.jpeg/U69YqUDmHsquZietTXvZM_3Sq7wTtRw_u1IRrJFSEaw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2F